div.div:
ShoppingCart will only add items when not completed. adding will also set total and tax to -1.
Calculate will always calculate unless complete is true.
CompletedTransactionException will be thrown whenever ShoppingCart has been completed to prevent double buying.
total and tax will have an initial value of -1. calculateFinalTotal() will run calculateTotal() and calculateTax() if total and tax equal -1 respectively.
if calculateTotal or calculateTax are called while complete is true, then they will return total and tax. calculateTotal nor calculateTax should never return -1. Instead throw an Error.
